msgid "When using nginx, we recommend <link xlink:href=\"http://docs.gunicorn.org/en/latest/deploy.html\">gunicorn</link> as the WSGI host with an appropriate number of synchronous workers. When using Apache, we recommend <literal>mod_wsgi</literal> to host the dashboard."
