#: ./security-guide/section_case-studies-management-interfaces.xml:9(para)
msgid "Previously we discussed typical OpenStack management interfaces and associated backplane issues. We will now approach these issues by returning to the Alice and Bob case studies (See <xref linkend=\"introduction-to-case-studies\"/> ) where Alice is deploying a government cloud and Bob is deploying a public cloud each with different security requirements. In this section, we will look into how both Alice and Bob will address:"
