#: ./security-guide/section_continuous-systems-management.xml:314(para)
msgid "Combining configuration management and security auditing tools creates a powerful combination. The auditing tools will highlight deployment concerns. And the configuration management tools simplify the process of changing each system to address the audit concerns. Used together in this fashion, these tools help to maintain a cloud that satisfies security requirements ranging from basic hardening to compliance validation."
