msgid "OpenStack Mailing List, [OpenStack] nova-novnc SSL configuration - Havana. 2014. <link xlink:href=\"http://lists.openstack.org/pipermail/openstack/2014-February/005357.html\">OpenStack nova-novnc SSL Configuration</link>"
