#: ./security-guide/section_api-endpoint-configuration-recommendations.xml:92(para)
msgid "You should isolate API endpoint processes, especially those that reside within the public security domain should be isolated as much as possible. Where deployments allow, API endpoints should be deployed on separate hosts for increased isolation."
