#: ./security-guide/section_case-studies-system-documentation.xml:9(para)
msgid "Earlier in <xref linkend=\"introduction-to-case-studies\"/> we introduced the Alice and Bob case studies where Alice is deploying a government cloud and Bob is deploying a public cloud each with different security requirements. Here we discuss how Alice and Bob would address their system documentation requirements. The documentation suggested above includes hardware and software records, network diagrams, and system configuration details."
