msgid "Siwczak, Piotr. Some Practical Considerations for Monitoring in the OpenStack Cloud. 2012. <link xlink:href=\"http://www.mirantis.com/blog/openstack-monitoring/\">http://www.mirantis.com/blog/openstack-monitoring</link>"
