msgid "The OpenStack Management Utilities are open-source Python command-line clients that make API calls. There is a client for each OpenStack service (for example, <systemitem class=\"service\">nova</systemitem>, <systemitem class=\"service\">glance</systemitem>). In addition to the standard CLI client, most of the services have a management command-line utility which makes direct calls to the database. These dedicated management utilities are slowly being deprecated."
