msgstr ""

#: ./security-guide/section_networking-architecture.xml:25(para)
msgid "This service runs on the network node to service the Networking API and its extensions. It also enforces the network model and IP addressing of each port. The neutron-server and plugin agents require access to a database for persistent storage and access to a message queue for inter-communication."
msgstr ""

#: ./security-guide/section_networking-architecture.xml:35(term)
msgid "plugin agent (<systemitem class=\"service\">neutron-*-agent</systemitem>)"
msgstr ""

#: ./security-guide/section_networking-architecture.xml:38(para)
msgid "Runs on each compute node to manage local virtual switch (vswitch) configuration. The plug-in that you use determine which agents run. This service requires message queue access and depends on the plugin used."
